==English==
===Etymology===
[[Blend]] of '''[[crap]]''' and '''[[spectacular]]'''

===Adjective===

'''craptacular''' (''[[comparative]]'' '''more {{PAGENAME}}''', ''[[superlative]]'' '''most {{PAGENAME}}''')



[[Category:English adjectives]]


#(''coarse UK slang'') Intended to be perceived as [[spectacular]], but actually perceived as extremely poor quality.
#:''Her essay was absolutely '''craptacular'''.''

